    AXIOM_LTK(z:ACTUAL_POSITION, k:#PCS::MaxStepsUp) and 
    (((ACTUAL_POSITION + #PCS::MaxStepsUp)) <= #PCS::MaxPosition)) >>
;

<< ((ACTUAL_POSITION' = ((ACTUAL_POSITION + Delta))) and 
    E_MS() and 
    (Delta = #PCS::MaxStepsUp) and 
    (ACTUAL_POSITION >= 0) and
